name: FormComponents
tagline: Initialize HTML form elements for keeping their behavior but custom styling.
body:
FormComponents
==============

Initialize HTML form elements for keeping their behavior but custom styling.

# Component List:
* Text Input
* Email Input
* Tel Input
* Url Input
* Search
* Radios
* Checkboxes
* Textarea
* Selector
* File Picker
* Numeric Input
* Range Bar
* Switcher
* Buttons

# TODO:
* Mixins
* Angular modular
* Browsers compatibility testing

Author: Aaron Chuo (crazychuo@gmail.com)
